articles.title: Missing Clark, Fever soar past Lynx 74-59 to win WNBA Commissioner’s Cup - NBC Sports
articles.description: Natasha Howard had 16 points, 12 rebounds and four assists on Tuesday night as the Indiana Fever defeated the Minnesota Lynx 74-59 in the WNBA Commissioner’s Cup final.
